OL,3,CThe Cornwall artist's 5-year wait for
OL,4,Can accessible home
OL,6,FMichael, who has cerebral palsy, has
OL,7,Fbeen on the waiting list for an
OL,8,Faccessible home for five years
OL,10,FMore than 1,000 people are currently
OL,11,Fwaiting for accessible housing in
OL,12,FCornwall, but there are only 13
OL,13,Fproperties available, figures
OL,14,Fexclusively gathered by ITV show.
OL,16,FAcross Cornwall there are also more
OL,17,Fthan 320 people who need a home where
OL,18,Fthey can use their wheelchair inside
OL,19,Fand out. The council currently has
OL,20,Fnone available to bid on.
