OL,3,CThe Cornwall artist's 5-year wait for
OL,4,Can accessible home
OL,6,FMichael, who has cerebral palsy, has
OL,7,Fbeen on the waiting list for five
OL,8,Fyears searching for a one bedroom
OL,9,Fwheelchair accessible home.
OL,11,FA lack of provision means he is
OL,12,Fcurrently living with his parents
OL,13,Fwhere he struggles to get up and down
OL,14,Fthe stairs, often having to slide down
OL,15,Fon his bottom.
OL,17,FMichael says as a result he has seen
OL,18,Fhis body slowly deteriorate.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
