OL,3,CThe Cornwall artist's 5-year wait for
OL,4,Can accessible home
OL,6,FHe told ITV News West Country: "There
OL,7,Fare times when no one is around, so I
OL,8,Fhave to bump down the stairs which
OL,9,Fdoctors have told me not to do.
OL,11,F"It is painful and extremely tiring
OL,12,Fand I'm in so much pain that I can't
OL,13,Fphysically do what I was doing before."
OL,15,FHe claims that in the five years he
OL,16,Fhas been searching, only one
OL,17,Fwheelchair accessible home has been
OL,18,Favailable in Penzance to bid on.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
