OL,3,CThe Cornwall artist's 5-year wait for
OL,4,Can accessible home
OL,6,FBut he says when they went to look at
OL,7,Fthe property, it was on a main road
OL,8,Fwith no pavement, and had steps up to
OL,9,Fthe front door.
OL,11,FHe said: "Why do I have to be the one
OL,12,Fleft behind? The one forgotten about?
OL,14,F"All the accessible flats I've seen in
OL,15,FCornwall are for the over 55's or
OL,16,Fsheltered, so I can't bid on them.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
