OL,3,CThe Cornwall artist's 5-year wait for
OL,4,Can accessible home
OL,6,F"What it feels like is they're very
OL,7,Fhappy to wait for my parents to die or
OL,8,Fget so old that they can't do anything
OL,9,Fand then they have to worry because
OL,10,Fnow I exist!"
OL,12,FDisability Cornwall and the Isle of
OL,13,FScilly say they speak to many people
OL,14,Fin this situation.
OL,16,FLara O'Brien from the charity said:
OL,17,F"They make a property accessible in
OL,18,Ftheir eyes, but it's not necessarily
OL,19,Fwhat the person who is going to have
OL,20,Fthat property needs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
