OL,3,CThe Cornwall artist's 5-year wait for
OL,4,Can accessible home
OL,6,F"There needs to be a wider
OL,7,Funderstanding of what accessible
OL,8,Fmeans, and then it needs to be
OL,9,Fspecific for that person who will have
OL,10,Fthe property rather than a tick box
OL,11,Fexercise.
OL,13,F"The wait list is just so long and the
OL,14,Fdecision makers are not allocating
OL,15,Fthem where they are needed. You can be
OL,16,Fon the list for 5 or 6 years and in
OL,17,Fthat time a disability can deteriorate
OL,18,Fand effect your life."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
