OL,3,CThe Cornwall artist's 5-year wait for
OL,4,Can accessible home
OL,6,FCornwall Council said: "We sympathise
OL,7,Fwith residents looking for a home
OL,8,Fsuitable for their needs and in their
OL,9,Fpreferred area as Cornwall continues
OL,10,Fto face significant pressures on
OL,11,Fhousing.
OL,13,F"In circumstances where people are
OL,14,Fwaiting for a suitable property, we
OL,15,Fwill provide support to ensure they
OL,16,Fare the on the correct banding and to
OL,17,Fconsider all potential housing
OL,18,Fsolutions ` whether this be through
OL,19,Fsocial housing or through the private
OL,20,Frented market."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
