OL,3,CThe Cornwall artist's 5-year wait for
OL,4,Can accessible home
OL,6,FWe also spoke to Lucy Apple, she now
OL,7,Flives in a ground floor flat which
OL,8,Fmakes day-to-day life with her
OL,9,Fcondition a lot easier, but she told
OL,10,Fus she wasn't so lucky with the
OL,11,Fproperty she was living in before.
OL,13,FShe admits that her new home is still
OL,14,Fnot fully accessible, with the kitchen
OL,15,Fcupboards being to high for her to
OL,16,Freach without assistance. She went on
OL,17,Fto add that the accessibility of the
OL,18,Fhouse you end up in depends on "how
OL,19,Flucky you get".
